data.title: Emily Mclaughlin - Autographed Inscribed Photograph
data.meta_description: Emily Mclaughlin - Autographed Inscribed Photograph  - Item 89379. 5x8 photograph showing the actress in character as nurse Jesse Brewer from the daytime soap opera General Hospital.Inscribed Photograph signed: 'David-/Thank you for writing!/Take care and keep/well/Emily McLaughlin/(Jesse Brewer, R.N.)' in blue felt tip, Color 5x8. Shop for  Emily Mclaughlin related autographs, signed photographs, historical documents and manuscripts from the world's largest collection. Every purchase includes our industry recognized COA. Worldwide shipping available.
